  1		315k		304k
  2		423k		424k
  4		644k		1032k
  8		652k		1267k
  16		737k		1368k
  32		759k		1199k
  64		636k		1094k
  72		609k		993k

1 and 2 thread performance is similar with and without INVLPGB, because
INVLPGB is only used on processes using 4 or more CPUs simultaneously.

The number is the median across 5 runs.

